                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.6363 Amiranian/8: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Merriam</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-01-18T09:00:00+03:25"
                            >January 18, 1937—9 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 18—7:43 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. My No. 2, January 11, noon. The two concessions were presented to the Mejlis
                    yesterday. Ratification procedure is expected to occupy about 2 weeks. The texts
                    are being published in the local press.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Merriam</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
